      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in flawless, showroom condition, exhibiting unblemished paintwork and an interior that retains its original integrity. Meticulously maintained and rigorously inspected, this specimen represents an uncompromising standard of quality for the discerning collector. It is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of such distinguished pedigree and pristine mechanical standing.",
