      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it still has that 'new car' feel! It drives like a dream and looks stunning from every angle. I've taken such good care of it, and I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it just as much. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
