    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the sought-after Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox, providing precise shift gates and mechanical purity. The chassis is structurally pristine, benefiting from proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. All maintenance is current, including documented rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly reliability. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero panel gaps or paint imperfections, while the interior features supple Nappa leather with no bolster wear. A turn-key masterpiece for the collector who demands peak mechanical synchronization and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
