    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional example that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained by a single enthusiast owner and has spent its entire life in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paint is factory-original and flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains supple and tight, with no bolster wear or creasing, and the original carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete, chronological binder of all service records performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. Most recently, it received a full fluid flush and a new set of Michelin Pilot Sport tires. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen for the buyer who demands perfection. Two keys, original window sticker, and a clean title are ready for the next owner.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
