    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in pristine showroom condition, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance, offering the discerning collector a rare opportunity to acquire a truly impeccable asset. This is a definitive example of the model, devoid of any discernible wear and representing the pinnacle of its class.",
