      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of it, keeping it tucked away in the garage and keeping it spotless, and let me tell you, it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that feels and looks brand new without that dealership price tag, this is the one! Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
